meanings: (그러나, …하지만) but, however, (and) yet, still, though, although
(어쨌든, …간에) (whether...) or, or the like, or what not

vlive.english: Soil hand, poo-poo hand, dung hand...?

vlive.korean: 열다섯 번 더 볼 거거든 - 으...
vlive.english: I'll watch it 15 times more. - Oh my...

vlive.korean: [으... 응...?][- 어묵 출신이 어디...?] 어디 어묵이에요 그거?
vlive.english: [Huh...?][Where is the fish cake from?] Where does he get the fish cake from?

vlive.korean: [으 어머님 참 배우신 분...] - 앞서가는 - 그 이유가 뭔가요?
vlive.english: [Wow, her mother can see into the future...] - She's so progressive. - What was her reason?

examples.korean: 으~ 낮잠이 필요해. 하지만 도서관에서 낮잠 잘 때마다 느끼는 거지만 개운하지가 않아.
examples.english: Ugh I need a nap. But whenever I nap at the library, I don’t feel refreshed.

examples.korean: 으, 그 벌레 정말 역겹게 생겼군.
examples.english: Blech, the bug looks really disgusting.

examples.korean: 으... 다 한 것 같은데 아직 멀었네!
examples.english: Ugh... so near and yet so far!
